	Bug Fixes
	* t/Memory.t failed test on non-US locale due to different $! error message.

0.03	2010-11-28
	Bug Fixes
	* Tests fail when CPU::Z80::Assembler is installed, but version is old, 
	  (e.g. 'equ' not recognized)

